\c 5
\s Nzira dzinouyisa mufaro
\v 1 Ngwarira rutsoka rwako kana uchienda kuimba yaMwari; nokuti kuswedera kuzonzwa kunopfuura kubayira chibayiro chamapenzi; nokuti havazivi kuti vanoita zvakaipa.
\v 2 Usakurumidza nomuromo wako, mwoyo wako urege kukurumidza kutaura shoko pamberi paMwari; nokuti Mwari ari kudenga, iwe uri pasi; naizvozvo mashoko ako ngaave mashoma.
\v 3 Nokuti kurota kunouya namabasa mazhinji, nezwi rebenzi namashoko mazhinji.
\v 4 Kana uchinge wapikira Mwari mhiko, usanonoka kuiripa; nokuti iye haafariri mapenzi; ripa zvaunopika.
\v 5 Zviri nani kuti urege kupika, pakuti upike usingaripi.
\v 6 Usatendera muromo wako kutadzisa nyama yako; usati pamberi pomutumwa waMwari,"Yakanga iri mhosho;Mwari achatsamwireiko inzwi rako,akaparadza basa ramaoko ako?"
\p
\v 7 Nokuti pakurota kuzhinji napamashoko mazhinji pane zvisina maturo zvizhinji; asi iwe utye Mwari.
\p
\v 8 Kana uchiona murombo achimanikidzwa, nokururamisa nokururama zvichibviswa nesimba panyika, usashamiswa nazvo; nokuti mukuru kuvakuru vose anocherekedza; vamwe variko vakuru kwavari.
\v 9 Nokuti nyika inobatsirwa zvikuru nechinhu ichi, mambo anofarira kurimiwa kweminda.
\p
\v 10 Anoda sirivha, haangagutswi nesirivha, naiye anoda zvakawanda, haangagutswi nezvakawanda; naizvozvo hazvina maturo.
\v 11 Kana pfuma ichiwanda, vadyi vanowandawo; mwene wayo anobatsirvvei, asi kungoona nameso ake.
\p
\v 12 Hope dzomunhu, unobata, dzakanaka, kana achidya zvishoma kana zvizhinji; asi kuguta kwomupfumi hakumutenderi kuvata.
\p
\v 13 Kune chinhu chakaisvoipa, chandakaona pasi pezuva, pfuma inochengetwa nomwene wayo, ichimuonesa nhamo.
\p
\v 14 Pfuma iyo inopera nechinhu chakaipa chinomuwira; kana achinge abereka mwanakomana, haana chinhu muruoko rwake.
\p
\v 15 Sezvaakabuda mudumbu ramai vake, achadzokazve asina chinhu, sezvaakabuda; haana chaakatamburira, chaangatora, chaangaenda nacho muruoko rwake.
\p
\v 16 Nechinhu ichi chakaisvoipawo, kuti pazvose, sezvaakauya, saizvozvo achaendazve; zvino achawaneiko, zvaakatamburira mhepo?
\v 17 Mazuva ake osewo anodya murima, anotambudzika kwazvo; anourwere neshungu.
\p
\v 18 Tarirai, zvandakaona kuti zvakanaka, zvinofanira munhu, ndiko kuti adye, anwe, afarire zvinhu zvakanaka pakubata kwake kwose kwaanobata pasi pezuva, mazuva ose oupenyu hwake hwaakapiwa naMwari; nokuti ndiwo mugove wake.
\v 19 Munhu mumwe nomumwewo, akapiwa naMwari pfuma nezvakawanda, akapiwawo simba kuti azvidye nokutora icho chipo chin
\p kuna Mwari.
\v 20 Nokuti iye haangarangariri zvikuru mazuva oupenyu hwake, nokuti Mwari anopindura pamufaro womwoyo wake.
\p Zviri nani kuti urege kupika, pakuti upike usingaripi.
\v 6 Usatendera muromo wako kutadzisa nyama yako; usati pamberi pomutumwa waMwari, "Yakanga iri mhosho; Mwari achatsamwireiko izwi rako, akaparadza basa ramaoko ako?"
